{"tid":2463252,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[ViuTV] ERROR主持 最後一屆口罩小姐選舉 星期一至五 21:30-22:30(9)","createTime":"2021-03-26T14:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T14:24:29.000Z","uid":313584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ef00dd4f57675b6ea3e50c67ada506e7e7d218de","tid":2463252,"uid":313584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T14:22:06.000Z","msg":"【口罩小姐】ViuTV最後一屆口罩小姐選舉3月22日播出！40強名單出爐 佳麗全程戴口罩保持神秘<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情陰霾籠罩下，口罩成為市民不可或缺的日常生活用品。ViuTV亦因此舉行口罩小姐選舉，參賽佳麗全程戴口罩，與以往的選美比賽截然不同。今日ViuTV正式公布口罩小姐40強名單。為了保持神秘，佳麗除了戴口罩之外，在淘汰之前不會公開身份。節目將於3月22日開播，逢星期一至五晚上9點半播出。<br />\n<br />\n40位候選口罩小姐主要職業是模特兒、網紅和學生，不過亦有專業人士。而一眾佳麗的技能和興趣亦千奇百趣，有人以「含住水說話」作賣點，有人的興趣是「買口罩」，亦有身懷特別技能的參加者，如揸飛機。"},{"pid":"8921c30c45a2e228ffca7aaef251570bca4c8a63","tid":2463252,"uid":197985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T14:23:19.000Z","msg":"保錡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d8a89fbb58dd87d4f29b0405e372534b5c29a6","tid":2463252,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T14:24:17.000Z","msg":"咖哩有啲似pony <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98234ab8d7b409fdeceff718052e2cda97a6f397","tid":2463252,"uid":2974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T14:24:24.000Z","msg":"poki foul左個ex？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3e8e47fc7b0af4da50bf86225af45760fd9624","tid":2463252,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T14:24:29.000Z","msg":"山小辣ig?"}]}